commentable_entity.ask: Virginia DA charge Amber Heard with perjury
commentable_entity.title: Virginia DA charge Amber Heard with perjury
commentable_entity.description:
Amber Heard lied under oath in the Defamation trial in Virginia. Since she is a famous person nothing is being done about it. This needs to change. Anyone who lies under oath needs to face the consequences immediately. This has not happened with Amber. 

Please sign this petition so that justice can be served.
